title: Rock Hall Inductions move to New York; Cleveland still planned for 2018
text:
Rock Hall Inductions move to New York; Cleveland still planned for 2018 
Published By: Cleveland.com - Today 
The 2016 Rock and Roll Hall of Fame Induction Ceremony will take place in New York City next April, not Los Angeles, as previously planned....
